==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-exaggerate.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Verb===
'''to exaggerate'''
#to [[overstate]], to describe more than is [[fact]]
#: ''I've told you a [[billion]] times not to '''exaggerate'''!''

